  "detailed_description": "<h1>Christmas Edition</h1><p>Ready to save Christmas? <br>This is not just an update of 1001 Hugs three years later. It's a huge improvement of the game story, new Features map, achievements, leaderboard, 11 new challenging, fantastic levels, and more. <br>The game will be released October 26, 2022.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157020/extras/7c84b49629cb6af8855fb5f8130e0f1a.avif?t=1668081633\" width=800 height=204 /></span></p><br><h1>Easter Adventure Plans</h1><p>We are launching a Kickstarter project to develop a new theme of the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157020/extras/92c3111332fb786a5c4bcfcbe0d3a8fe.avif?t=1668081633\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157020/extras_big/92c3111332fb786a5c4bcfcbe0d3a8fe.avif?t=1668081633 width=800 height=440 /></span><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>1001 Hugs, version 2, has a new game story. <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Now you are in Elfland with a special mission to collect Christmas presents throughout 16 levels and bring them to Santa.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">To pass levels you need to open portals; to do that you hug 4 key elves, and in return they get a candy cane. </ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">But you have only 1001 candy canes. Elves try to stop you by making you lose them before you reach Santa! </ul>Some elves just refuse to hug. You have to come up with a hugging strategy to get to Santa with gifts and leftover candy canes.<br>It's an adventure with lots of hugs, pitter patter of little feet, laughter and giggles, slamming doors, flying teddy bears, bursting water balloons, and slippery puddles! <br><br>New in this version:<br>+ Game story<br>+ 11 more beautiful and challenging levels<br>+ Features map with detailed game rules<br>+ Multiple achievements<br>+ Scoring and leaderboard<br>+ Character customization<br>+ Player's outfits, hats, teddy bear launchers, and packsacks<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157020/extras/736d0f82df2046e6446547bcf3fd4561.avif?t=1668081633\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157020/extras_big/736d0f82df2046e6446547bcf3fd4561.avif?t=1668081633 width=800 height=448 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157020/extras/043bd69f13d665b1b7c21a8a86d3181a.avif?t=1668081633\" width=800 height=528 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157020/extras/fc022cb1687565879f1d52ab22287125.avif?t=1668081633\" width=800 height=522 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157020/extras/c1c7298761575574d947152a5e4b4773.avif?t=1668081633\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157020/extras_big/c1c7298761575574d947152a5e4b4773.avif?t=1668081633 width=800 height=448 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157020/extras/b3ddc0a8054ab0797ab683c6749648eb.avif?t=1668081633\" width=800 height=502 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157020/extras/4f47026b2c4a490d4a244cce49a071a9.avif?t=1668081633\" width=800 height=496 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157020/extras/8a10392dc0f2d5a9aca2907374d6145b.avif?t=1668081633\" width=800 he